{"type":null,"faqId":46535,"title":"How can I block notifications from a particular app? How can I unblock notifications after they have been disabled?","answer":"<body style=\"clear:both; padding-left:10px; padding-top:5px; padding-right:5px; padding-bottom:5px\"><a name=\"EN-US_TOPIC_0020255174\"></a><a name=\"EN-US_TOPIC_0020255174\"></a><div id=\"body1443167062212\"><p id=\"EN-US_TOPIC_0020255174__p21869070164932\"><strong id=\"EN-US_TOPIC_0020255174__b54479043164947\">To block notifications from an app:</strong></p><p id=\"EN-US_TOPIC_0020255174__p62603902164932\"><strong id=\"EN-US_TOPIC_0020255174__b26564211164932\">Method 1: </strong>Go to the settings screen in the Android Wear app and then add the app that you want to block to the <strong id=\"EN-US_TOPIC_0020255174__b37751308164932\">Block app notifications</strong> list.</p><p id=\"EN-US_TOPIC_0020255174__p4217460164932\"><strong id=\"EN-US_TOPIC_0020255174__b37957147164932\">Method 2: </strong>Swipe right on a push notification and then touch <strong id=\"EN-US_TOPIC_0020255174__b6070011164932\">Block app</strong> to block notifications for that app.</p><p id=\"EN-US_TOPIC_0020255174__p54630099164932\"><strong id=\"EN-US_TOPIC_0020255174__b2174543164950\">To unblock notifications:</strong></p><p id=\"EN-US_TOPIC_0020255174__p21908845164932\">Go to the settings screen in the Android Wear app and then delete the apps that you want to unblock from the <strong id=\"EN-US_TOPIC_0020255174__b62961883164932\">Block app notifications</strong> list.</p></div><div><div class=\"familylinks\"></div></div></body>","faqTypeId":329,"faqType":"SIM Card, SMS, Calls, and Contacts","useful":1,"unUseful":0,"languageId":1,"languageName":"en","faqCode":"en-us_topic_0020255174","faqTypeCode":"Wearable_Device-SIM-SMS-Calls-Contacts","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1444639610000,"seriesProductName":"Mercury-G00,Mercury-G01,Mercury-G10","visitedTimes":51,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"app, block, notification, unblock","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}